OL,3,CInvestigation reveals true extent of
OL,4,CNazi atrocities in Alderney
OL,6,FAn investigation has revealed the true
OL,7,Fextent of Nazi war crimes committed
OL,8,Fagainst slave workers shipped to the
OL,9,FChannel Island of Alderney during the
OL,10,FSecond World War.
OL,12,FFindings published in a new report
OL,13,Fcommissioned by UK Holocaust Envoy
OL,14,FLord Pickles reveal that a maximum of
OL,15,F1,134 prisoners died, with the
OL,16,Fprobable range of between 641 and
OL,17,F1,027.
