OL,3,CInvestigation reveals true extent of
OL,4,CNazi atrocities in Alderney
OL,6,FThat is far greater than the previous
OL,7,Fofficial figure of 389 that had been
OL,8,Festimated after a study of unmarked
OL,9,Fgraves several decades ago.
OL,11,FThe purpose of the investigation was
OL,12,Fto finally decide a true figure of how
OL,13,Fmany people died during the German
OL,14,FOccupation and to, in the words of
OL,15,FLord Eric Pickles, "provide dignity to
OL,16,Fthe dead and peace to the people of
OL,17,FAlderney, who continue to remember
OL,18,Fthem."
