OL,3,CInvestigation reveals true extent of
OL,4,CNazi atrocities in Alderney
OL,6,FMore than 7,000 slave workers from
OL,7,Faround 30 different nationalities were
OL,8,Fshipped to Alderney during the
OL,9,FOccupation to build fortifications for
OL,10,FHitler's Atlantic Wall.JThese
OL,11,Findividuals were largely kept in
OL,12,Flabour camps, where they endured
OL,13,Fstarvation, long working hours,
OL,14,Fbeatings, maiming, torture and, in
OL,15,Fsome cases, executions.JResearchers
OL,16,Fhave found evidence that suggests, on
OL,17,Fa few occasions, bodies were even
OL,18,Fdumped into the sea.
