OL,3,CInvestigation reveals true extent of
OL,4,CNazi atrocities in Alderney
OL,6,FHowever, claims that Alderney
OL,7,Fconstituted a 'mini-Auschwitz' remain
OL,8,Fwholly unsubstantiated, and there is
OL,9,Fno evidence that the island ever
OL,10,Fhoused an extermination camp.
OL,12,FDespite the suffering inflicted,
OL,13,Fvirtually none of the German
OL,14,Fperpetrators were ever brought to
OL,15,Fjustice, because it has emerged that
OL,16,Fin September 1945, the British
OL,17,Fgovernment handed the case over to the
OL,18,FUSSR, who did nothing with it.
